300
00:19:57,180 --> 00:19:58,940
In this land of many mysteries,

301
00:19:58,940 --> 00:20:03,100
it's a strange fact that the largest legends seem to collect around the smallest creatures.

302
00:20:04,300 --> 00:20:06,940
