303
00:20:08,540 --> 00:20:10,540
Here's an actual living legend.

304
00:20:10,540 --> 00:20:14,140
For it's set of this tiny animal that it commits mass suicide

305
00:20:14,140 --> 00:20:15,900
by rushing into the sea in droves.

306
00:20:21,100 --> 00:20:25,100
In 1958, Disney put out a film called White Wilderness,

307
00:20:25,100 --> 00:20:27,740
a documentary of life at the poles.

308
00:20:28,620 --> 00:20:30,860
These days, it's infamous for one scene.

309
00:20:31,580 --> 00:20:33,740
Contrary to the narrator's insistence,

310
00:20:33,740 --> 00:20:37,660
